short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Allows you to use the Middlebury Go servive off campus without typing go.middlebury.edu/

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Middlebury Go extension redirects urls that start with go/* to go.middlebury.edu/*.  This allows you to use the Go Link system anywhere in the world without connecting to the Middlebury network.
